{
  "stem": "2533.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used, not to socialize, but but to talk, to- to keep-- we had friends together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even to a certain time of night, before they switched the lights off, everybody had to be in the barracks, even with the men and the boys, we were outside our sleeping quarters.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until a certain hour, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the boys, yes, you know, because we couldn't speak like Dutch or German, but a lot of the Polish or from Czechoslovakia, they spoke really, really German.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we learned from Yiddish, you know, too, but we didn't want to speak Yiddish in the camp because we didn't want that the SS men will pick up some words.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when we were speaking about ourselves, it was in Polish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the other nationalities were speaking in their own language.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If they knew German, maybe there was German there too, from Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a girl, more than one, and men were there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One couple was a German couple.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a beast too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we used to be, like, together, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We used to help out each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, but we knew all what was happened, and we couldn't speak to the Dutch people, because we wouldn't-- they wouldn't understand us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the German, the one who could speak German, we used to-- to-- to-- oh, what's her name?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She spoke so good German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then Mrs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Schildkraut, she spoke German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Mira-- oh, she spoke like a German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They used to socialize with the other, who could understand each other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It wasn't like in the big, big camp, maybe like in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't steal from each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't hate each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And whatever were working, we try just to be not-- maybe even friends.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
